	<!--Name of the mod to display to players-->
	<DisplayName Value="LOD Control" />
	<!--Short description of the mod-->
	<ShortDescription Value="Change LOD distance higher than vanilla allows" />
	<!--Long description of the mod. Single line or multi line. Supports minimal markdown subset-->
	<!--LongDescription Value="This is a long description" /-->
	<LongDescription>
Level of detail makes a huge difference in graphics. The game allows you to choose values from 10% to 100%. This mod increases the maximum to 1000%. Also adds a toggle to disable LODs completely.
Playing with disabled LODs is not really possible, but it's useful for creating screenshots.
		
## Features
- Adjust LOD distance from 0% to 1000% of vanilla values
- Setting to disable LODs completely
- Hotkey to enable/disable LODs (usable from photo mode)
		
Images show 50%, 100%, 500% and LODs disabled
	</LongDescription>
